514
00:49:09,212 --> 00:49:10,509
Yes, I do.

515
00:49:10,681 --> 00:49:14,879
Yeah, look, marriages end.
I'm sorry, but I didn't end yours.

516
00:49:15,052 --> 00:49:16,883
