635
01:00:13,109 --> 01:00:16,272
This whole thing is out of your
control now. You know it, I know it.

636
01:00:16,446 --> 01:00:18,778
You started this shit,
I'm gonna finish it.

637
01:00:19,816 --> 01:00:23,650
